---
title: Mom’s Magic One-Pot Chicken Noodle Soup with Mixed Veggies, Lemon & Dill
description: Maybe you had a mom who made you chicken noodle soup. Maybe you didn’t. Either way, now you can make it for yourself! Tonight’s soup is the warm liquid gold that’s just what you’d imagine a mother’s hug in food form to be. Filled with extra veggies (broccoli, cauliflower, and carrot), each bowl is flavorful and oh-so soothing. For the noodles, we opted for broken spaghetti, making each spoonful extra slurpable.
